      <title>SEB 交易员对预期大幅降息反应平淡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/seb-traders-see-muted-reactions-for-expected-jumbo-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典北欧斯安银行（SEB AB）交易员表示，瑞典央行本周可能会加快宽松步伐，他们预计周四央行决定宣布后，市场波动将有限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/seb-traders-see-muted-reactions-for-expected-jumbo-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 07:51:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
